.display__list
/product_pathのところは商品詳細ページに飛ぶようなパスに名前を書き換える
  - @products.each do |product|
    = link_to product_path(product.id) do
      .display__pic
        - if product.images.present?
          .imgpic
            = image_tag (product.images[0].product_image.url)
        -else
          = image_tag "no_image.png"
        /productテーブルにbuyer_idを追加必要？ダメなら他に売り切れか判断するメソッド
        -if product.buyer_id.present?
          .items-box_photo__sold
            .items-box_photo__sold__inner
              SOLD
        .display__body
          %h3.display__name
            = product.name
          .display__details
            %ul.display__content
              = "¥ #{product.price.to_s(:delimited)}"
              %li.fa.fa-star.likeIcon 0
            %p (税込)

